{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01CwmnEbk4h2gZUq23jt7qJE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01D2bhmfRXT8kKEm84LVT8Uu","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/verification/17-1-worktree-manager-proof.md","content":"# Verification Proof: 17-1-worktree-manager\n\nDate: 2026-04-03\nTier: runtime-provable\nVerdict: ALL_PASS\n\n## Build & Test Summary\n\n- **Build:** PASS (`npm run build` completes without errors)\n- **Full suite:** PASS (4813 tests passed across 178 files, 0 failures)\n- **Focused tests:** PASS (33/33 tests in `worktree-manager.test.ts`)\n- **Coverage:** 98.21% statements, 86.48% branches, 100% functions, 99.07% lines (uncovered: line 120 — defensive unreachable branch)\n\n## AC 1: createWorktree creates branch from main\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n**Evidence:**\nTest \"creates branch and worktree, returns path (AC #1, #2)\" verifies `git branch codeharness/epic-17-worktree-manager main` is called via execSync mock. Code at line 103: `this.execGit(\\`git branch ${branchName} ${this.mainBranch}\\`)`.\n```output\nexpect(calls).toContainEqual(expect.stringContaining('git branch codeharness/epic-17-worktree-manager main')) ✓\n```\n\n## AC 2: createWorktree creates worktree and returns path\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n**Evidence:**\nTest \"creates branch and worktree, returns path (AC #1, #2)\" verifies worktree created at `/tmp/codeharness-wt-epic-17` and return value matches. Code at line 107: `this.execGit(\\`git worktree add ${worktreePath} ${branchName}\\`)`.\n```output\nexpect(path).toBe('/tmp/codeharness-wt-epic-17') ✓\nexpect(calls).toContainEqual(expect.stringContaining('git worktree add /tmp/codeharness-wt-epic-17 codeharness/epic-17-worktree-manager')) ✓\n```\n\n## AC 3: createWorktree completes in under 10 seconds (runtime-provable)\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n**Evidence:**\nRuntime timing test on a real git repo: `git worktree add` completed in 0.025