{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CSWPMFUpzH5f1SnBgmhEhE","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03 (Session 8)\n2\t\n3\t## Prior Sessions (Summary)\n4\t\n5\tSessions 1-6 completed all Epic 16 stories (16-1 through 16-6). Session 7 completed create-story, dev-story, and code-review for 17-1-worktree-manager. Key recurring issues:\n6\t- `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` path incorrect (actual: `_bmad/config.yaml`)\n7\t- `codeharness coverage --min-file 80` broken due to pre-existing stats.test.ts failure\n8\t- AGENTS.md consistently missing new file entries\n9\t- Pre-existing tsc errors in unrelated files\n10\t- Proof format headers frequently wrong on first attempt (`### AC #N:` vs `## AC N:`)\n11\t\n12\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0d8bd255-97e7-4ce2-b430-6ab2ab2aca0a","uuid":"ba763598-12ec-4195-b792-b22bd4d99cce","timestamp":"2026-04-03T19:58:16.765Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03 (Session 8)\n\n## Prior Sessions (Summary)\n\nSessions 1-6 completed all Epic 16 stories (16-1 through 16-6). Session 7 completed create-story, dev-story, and code-review for 17-1-worktree-manager. Key recurring issues:\n- `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` path incorrect (actual: `_bmad/config.yaml`)\n- `codeharness coverage --min-file 80` broken due to pre-existing stats.test.ts failure\n- AGENTS.md consistently missing new file entries\n- Pre-existing tsc errors in unrelated files\n- Proof format headers frequently wrong on first attempt (`### AC #N:` vs `## AC N:`)\n\n","numLines":12,"startLine":1,"totalLines":12}}}
